<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.10">
<l>aṭiyārnta vaiyamuṇ ṭālilai yaṉṉavacañ ceyyum</l>
<l>paṭiyātu milkuḻa vipaṭi yentai pirāṉṟaṉak</l>
<l>kaṭiyā raṭiyār tammaṭi yāraṭi yārtamak</l>
<l>kaṭiyā raṭiyār tammaṭi yāraṭi yōṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We are the servants of the servants of the servants of the servants</l>
<l>of the servants of the servants of the servants of the servants</l>
<l>of the lord our father on earth as a child without any equal</l>
<l>who takes a nap on the fig leaf after having swallowed the world full of feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
